10. Troubleshooting and Best Practices
- Tests failing due to Node version mismatch: ensure CI uses Node >= 24.0.0, update engine in CI matrix.
- Unexpected character counts: confirm iteration is using code points (for...of) not code units (string[i]).
- Bit counting errors for large integers: switch Number inputs to BigInt and use BigInt XOR and popcount.
- Workflows cannot modify .github/workflows/: verify WORKFLOW_TOKEN exists and is used by init workflow.
- If agentic infra changes are not applied: run npx @xn-intenton-z2a/agentic-lib@latest init locally to pull updates.
- Avoid committing secrets; ensure tokens are stored in repository Secrets.

